## Product Requirements Document

The full PRD is at `context/foundation/prd.md`. Reference it with `@context/foundation/prd.md` when you need the complete document.

### Key Facts

- Product: Pomodoro + adaptive-focus web-app for knowledge workers
- Auth: login required (email/password, OAuth, passwordless), flat role model
- Core loop: task list → Pomodoro cycle → mindful check-in → next-task suggestion
- 22 functional requirements across: Authentication (FR-001–003a), Task List (FR-004–009a), Pomodoro (FR-010–015), Delight (FR-016), Adaptive Focus (FR-017–022)

### When to Load Full PRD

- Implementing a new feature — check FR numbers and acceptance criteria
- Writing tests — verify expected behavior against user stories
- Making UX decisions — check non-functional requirements (200ms response, ±2s timer accuracy)
- Scoping work — check non-goals to avoid building out-of-scope features
